General.Name: TEK Ocean Group Ltd
General.Description: TEK-Ocean Group Limited provides integrated services for the oil, gas, marine, and renewable energy sectors in Australia. The company provides renewable energy services; marine and subsea services; logistics and supply base services; engineering and project management services; and consultancy and personnel services. It also offers oilfield services, including machine shop, workshop, aftermarket, asset management, preservation, and storage services. In addition, the company provides rental equipment services. TEK-Ocean Group Limited was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Melbourne, Australia.
